analyze-config1.json  
--------------------
analyze an entire directory of files containing expression data.
run anova,williams and curvefit prefilters
then run 2 different BMDS MLE analyses
then run go, pathway and defined category analysis on each bmd analysis output


analyze-config2.json
--------------------

analyze an entire directory of files containing expression data.
run curvefit prefilters
then run 2 different BMDS MLE analyses
then run 2 different ToxicR Model Averaging analyses (1 laplace and 1 mcmc)
then run go, pathway and defined category analysis on each bmd analysis output



analyze-config3.json
--------------------
analyace individual files using the configuration to control the naming.




